@{U}umatrix()@{UU}

@{B}sypnosis:@{UB}
   @{B}umatrix(@{I}n @{UI})@{UB}

@{B}arguments:@{UB}
   @{I}n @{UI}: positive integer

@{B}result:@{UB}
   matrix

   This will create a standart matrix of the given size.


@{FG SHINE}@{BG SHADOW}@{B}------------------------------------------------------------------ © by P!\K -@{FG TEXT}@{BG BACKGROUND}@{UB}
